    <data key="d0">ContactSuite Scalable Contact Center Platform</data>
    <data key="d1">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BPvr0qWpJlA</data>
    <data key="d2">A scalable contact center platform built with Amazon Connect, utilizing ECS microservices for CRM integrations, EC2 ASG for the agent portal, and RDS/DynamoDB for storage.</data>
